  "remarks": "CDi.017 Designation: Former DFLR Vice President. Arrested by German authorities on 17 November 2009,  found guilty in a German court on 28 September 2015 of leadership of a foreign terrorist group, and received an 8-year sentence. Musoni was released from prison immediately after the trial, having served over 5 years of his sentence.; Listing: Listed by 1533 Committee on: 29 Mar. 2007 (amended on 13 Oct. 2016)",
